ut the ultimate victory\nof the legitf.mistic principle.\nNotice to Holders of\nFOURTH Liberty Loan Bonds\nNow is the time to exchange\nyour temporary bonds for per\nmanent bonds. Delivery to be\nmade about January 15, 1921\nLET US SERVE YOTJ\nThe First Bridgeport-National Bank\nMain and State Streets\nv\njo6t MainStaJidi4itoi49l3irIfeIcAve.\nBridgeport Busy Cash Store\nerwear in Good Varieties\nNo matter what the particular style or fabric a man de\nsires, in Underwear, we have what we consider a fine showing,'\nin weight and quality that will satisfy him. They are the\nkind that will keep a man comfortable throughout the raw cold\ndays of the next two months.\nMen's Cotton ribbed Union Suits, 1. $2.15\nMen's Part Wool Union Suits $2.65\nMen's Cotton ribbed Shirt and Drawers $1.00 each\nMen's Cotton and Wool Shirts and Drawers $1.65 each\nMen's Fleeced Lined Shirts and Drawers $1.39 each\nBlack and Flowered Sateen Fecticoats\nAt Interesting Prices\nYou can't really condemn designers of Petticoats for cutting\nthem out of Sateen. This ideal Petticoat Material has proved its\nserviceable qualities by the extent of the demands. We are offer\ning two special Bargains, that should interest many women from\nan economical standpoint.\nBlack Sateen Petticoats, of excellent heavy quality. There are\nregular and extra sizes in the lot. Some have the dust ruffle,\nwhile others a fancy ruffle. Special $1.39\nFlowered Sateen Petticoats,, in regular sizes only. rShown in\na pleasing assortment of patterns. i Special lmQQ\nTheSmithMurrayCa\nMen's-Und\nLOWER PRICES\nAt\nMOL LAN'S\nWomen's Dorothy Dodd and\nGrover smart boots in grey,\nbrown and black, in latest t'\nmodels, included in ?12 and $13\nlines, for\nTEN DOLLARS\nWomen's natty outdoor boots,\nbrown calf, included in $15\nlines, for\nv. TWELVE DOLLARS\nNewest Black Satin Evening\nSlippers with instep strap and\nLouis or baby Louis heel, v$5.00.\nWith ankle strap and Louis\nbeel $5.50'\n1026 MAIN ST.\ni\no meiavji nervous u