ved at\nany hour of the day or night.\nL5a\nM. J. GANNON\nFUNERAL DIRECTOR\nAND E, MBALMER\n315 John Street\n'Phone 3493\nResidence 235 Vine St.\nPhone 1259\nM ONUMENTS-\nand Polishing Tools\n100 STRATFORD AVENUE\nARTISTIC LASTING\nPlant Operated by Pneumatic Cutting\nHUGHES CHAPMAN\nPhone Connection\nBRIDGEPORTS BUSY\nCHIROPRACTOR.\nNEWFIEU5 &UDG\nBARNUM 4907\nT. B, WARREN\nReal Estate and Insurance\nJ 1089 Broad Street\nTel. Bar. 621\nWhy You Should\nZAT FRISBIK S PIES\nThey are Pare\nMade Clean\nHomelike\nWholesome.\nInsist ew JSYtehle'B -Jfwue on every\nPlo. At Ton Grocer and Restaur-\nantl\nMargaret John\nGALLAGHER GALLAGHER\nGraduate and Licensed\nUndertakers and Embalmers\nMargaret L. Gallagher, only li\ncensed graduate woman embalm\ner and undertaker in the city.\nMortuary parlors, offices and res.\n571 Fairfield Ave. Phone Bar. 1390\nGEORGE P. POTTER\nUNDERTAKER\nAutomobile Service If Preferred.\nMORTUARY ROOMS\n113 3 BROAD STREET\nTet Bar. 6848-2.\nPATENTS\na ivr wnneTfo\nFormerly Examiner TJ.S. Patent OOtoa\nSend for Booklets on Patents.\nSCHOOL SUPPLIES\nSeheol Baea, Pencil Sots, Book Stntpe,\npads, Loose Leaf Sheets, Fountain\nPens, Paperoid Envelopes suitable fdr\ncarrytns aebool papers now on safe\n-Post Office Ne-Brs Store\n11 Peat Office Arcade\nS. LOEWITH CO.\ni?ro.\nLSLRA.CE\nREAL ESTATE\nRENTS\nSTEAMSHIP TICKETS\nFOREIGN MONEY ORDERS\n116 BsLnk St., Bridgeport\nTel. Bar. 99. Est. 1865\nB 11 tt.\nSANITARY BEDDING Co.\nSALESROOMS C03 HAIUlAIi AVE.\nManufacturers of all kinds of bed\nding. Specialists in Silk Floss and\nHair Mattresses. We also remodel\nall kinds of mattresses. Mail and\nphone, orders taken.\nFACTORY 469 CATHERINE ST. -Telephone\nNoble 1726-2","height":"26560","width":"21348"}}
